Sum==k (Any numbers) : Prefix Sum + HashMap
Sum (>=, >, <, <=) k (0 and Positive Numbers Only) : Sliding Window
Sum (>=, >, <, <=) K (Any numbers) : Prefix Sum + Monotonic Stack
Max/Min Sum (Any numbers) : Kadane's Algorithm
Product (Any numbers) : Modified Kadane's (track min & max)
Majority (Count > K) : Transform array to +-1 then : Prefix Sum + HashMap
