Summary Checklist:
Check the values: Are there negative numbers?
No negatives: Use Sliding Window.
Negatives present: Use Monotonic Stack or HashMap.

Check the goal:
Equality: HashMap.
Inequality: Sliding Window (if positive) or Monotonic Stack (if negative).
